==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: identifying
<hw>identifying</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>serving to
distinguish or identify an object, person, species or group; <as>as, we
were asked to describe any <ex>identifying</ex> marks or distinguishing
features</as>.</def> <mark>[prenominal]</mark>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> distinguishing, distinctive.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

